explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the validity of the Capital Asset Pricing Model (CAPM) and the Fama French Three Factor Model (FF3) in the Indian equity market, using statistical methods like the Fama-Macbeth Methodology of two pass regression. It does not mention or involve any machine learning techniques, neural networks, or related concepts from the provided keyword list. The study is purely based on financial econometrics and does not utilize any of the specified machine learning or deep learning methodologies.
